323
00:25:40,212 --> 00:25:42,474
[SPEAKER_07]: I believe very passionately in a...

324
00:25:43,215 --> 00:25:44,236
[SPEAKER_07]: I use the NHS.

325
00:25:44,296 --> 00:25:44,636
[SPEAKER_07]: I love it.

326
00:25:44,676 --> 00:25:47,038
[SPEAKER_07]: It's one of the most incredible things about this country.

327
00:25:47,199 --> 00:25:48,320
[SPEAKER_07]: It is admired around the world.

328
00:25:48,500 --> 00:25:51,983
[SPEAKER_07]: The central idea that if any of us get sick, all of us take care of them.

329
00:25:52,123 --> 00:25:53,104
[SPEAKER_07]: It's a fantastic thing.

330
00:25:53,344 --> 00:26:01,913
[SPEAKER_07]: Now, we believe in an NHS free at the point of use, and under no circumstances will we sell it off to anybody in any kind of trade deal.

