543
00:43:14,274 --> 00:43:19,148
[SPEAKER_07]: Automatic early release in such cases is, I think, completely unreasonable and we will get rid of it.

544
00:43:19,168 --> 00:43:22,918
[SPEAKER_09]: Could you address Mr Corbyn's point, though, that you have decimated

