559
00:44:29,984 --> 00:44:34,570
[SPEAKER_08]: So you end up with a breeding ground for all the horrors of the future.

560
00:44:34,550 --> 00:44:37,554
[SPEAKER_08]: If we go down that road, we all pay a price.

561
00:44:37,574 --> 00:44:47,167
[SPEAKER_08]: So I'm simply saying this, let's invest in our prison system, invest in rehabilitation, invest crucially in a probation service that works.

562
00:44:47,387 --> 00:44:51,813
[SPEAKER_08]: It was privatised by this government and we're saying it should be completely in public ownership.

563
00:44:51,833 --> 00:44:53,576
